="https://www.nme.com/news/music/doja-cat-to-headline-rock-in-rio-lisbon-2024-3556411">Doja Cat</a> 。今年是该节日的 20 周年纪念日，该节日在可容纳 80,000 人的 Parque Tejo Lisboa 举办。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/camila-cabello">卡米拉·卡贝洛</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/evanescence">伊凡塞斯</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/extreme">Extreme</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/calum-scott">卡勒姆·斯科特</a>、路易莎·桑扎、佩德罗·桑帕约、Jão 和费尔南多·丹尼尔也已宣布参演。门票现已发售——请点击<a href="https://rockinriolisboa.pt/en/tickets" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>购买。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ed-sheeran-wins-his-first-emmy-for-his-ted-lasso-song-3566757">艾德·希兰 (Ed Sheeran) 凭借歌曲《Ted Lasso》赢得了他的第一个艾美奖，该消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
